    <a title="Amanda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8021133-amanda"><img alt="Amanda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1400379151p2/8021133.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/809387032?book_show_action=true">Jan 02, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amanda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amanda" href="/user/show/8021133-amanda">Amanda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8021133-amanda?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer809387032" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18204627937719474155">Re-read 11/25/19-4/12/20<br/><br/>Re-read for book club 7/4- /16<br/><br/>Read 7/23-27/14: I&apos;m sitting here, at a loss for what to say about this book. Because anything I can express in words would just not be enough to convey what this book means and how it has affected me. Wow.</span>
  <span id="freeText18204627937719474155" style="display:none">Re-read 11/25/19-4/12/20<br /><br />Re-read for book club 7/4- /16<br /><br />Read 7/23-27/14: I'm sitting here, at a loss for what to say about this book. Because anything I can express in words would just not be enough to convey what this book means and how it has affected me. Wow.</span>
  <a data-text-id="18204627937719474155" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

